_:N0950b8af544b4529b84063200f7c441b <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Adam Land was appointed Senior Director of the Office for the Internal Market and the Subsidy Advice Unit on 1 July 2024.</p>\n\n<p>Before being appointed to this role, Adam was Senior Director of Remedies, Business and Financial Analysis at the CMA and has previously worked in a variety of roles in competition policy and HM Treasury. Adam chairs the Health and Wellbeing Senior Steering Group for the UK Civil Service.</p>\n" .
